<node id="&quot;BEEKEEPERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Beekeepers are individuals who engage in the practice of keeping honeybees, requiring preparation, ongoing attention, and commitment."&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeepers are individuals who regularly handle bees and are at risk of being stung multiple times."</data>
