  <data key="d1">"Knowledge is a key attribute of a successful beekeeper."&lt;SEP&gt;"Knowledge refers to the accumulated understanding of bees and beekeeping practices, which has increased significantly in recent years."&lt;SEP&gt;"Knowledge refers to the understanding of bees, growing things, and the natural world needed for successful beekeeping."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-2ff401080e75bc199ec4bbb83221e314&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
