<node id="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A beekeeper is an individual who manages and cares for honey bee colonies, often for the purpose of producing honey or pollinating crops."&lt;SEP&gt;"A beekeeper is someone who keeps bees, often with a high level of commitment and knowledge."&lt;SEP&gt;"A beekeeper is someone who manages and cares for honeybees, typically experiencing mild reactions to bee stings."&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;"Beekeeper is a person who manages and cares for bee colonies, relying on the bees' dance language for information."</data>
