  <data key="d1">"Transferee Joinder is a document executed by a Transferee to join the agreement as a Supporting Lender."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transferee Joinder is a written agreement that binds Transferees to the terms of the agreement after receiving transferred Prepetition Agreement Claims."</data>
