<node id="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Company is a business entity involved in a transfer of claims and agreements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is a business entity mentioned in the text, possibly related to legal proceedings involving claims and liens."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity filing motions and pleadings with the Bankruptcy Court and consulting with Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity receiving notifications from the Supporting Lenders regarding events that may affect the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the entity that supports and does not object to changes or withdrawals of votes by Supporting Lenders, as required by the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company is the main party agreeing to commitments during the Effective Period, including seeking approval of the Plan and completing the Restructuring."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is subject to various conditions and obligations outlined in the agreement, including the exclusive right to file and solicit acceptances of a chapter 11 plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that is subject to various conditions and restrictions in the agreement, including mergers, dispositions, and other transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the entity that supports and does not object to changes or withdrawals of votes or releases as per the agreement terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main business entity mentioned in the text, which needs to comply with certain conditions and possess necessary permits."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity mentioned in the text, which is subject to various conditions and compliance requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company refers to the main entity mentioned in the text, which is subject to various legal and regulatory requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is the entity that may withdraw or revoke the Plan, file alternative transactions, or support other plans that are inconsistent with the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c27bf2a240355db951cca111fcbf0b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3118a5b7ebfcd2e890ae61fb2869a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b75be069c2e11b99b8211d14f57d5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecc6c7a82dfa782ad734c65afdc66563&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09b10f93e9533caaeadef2357fac4779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f645c16a1cbf2169e4377767b2bca09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PREPETITION AGREEMENT CLAIMS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Prepetition Agreement Claims are specific claims that exist before a bankruptcy filing and are subject to transfer and agreement terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Prepetition Agreement Claims refer to claims held by the relevant Transferee before a certain agreement is consummated."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 28}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 72}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PREPETITION AGENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Prepetition Agents are entities that represent the Company in prepetition matters."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;FEREE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Feree is a term used to describe a transferee or a supporting lender in the context of the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ORDER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Order is a legal directive issued by the Bankruptcy Court that may limit transfers of claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"Order refers to a formal directive issued by the Bankruptcy Court."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 28}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 71}, {"level": 3, "cluster": 94}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BUSINESS DAY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Business Day is a specific period during which financial transactions can occur."&lt;SEP&gt;"Business Day refers to a day on which banks and financial institutions are open for business."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CLAIM&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Claim is a specific right or demand that a party has against another party, often monetary in nature."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 28}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 72}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PARTY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Party is a generic term referring to any entity involved in the agreement, such as the Company, Supporting Lender, or Transferee."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 28}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 72}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Representations and Warranties are statements made by a party in an agreement that are intended to be true and accurate."&lt;SEP&gt;"Representations and Warranties are the assurances given by the Supporting Lenders regarding the truthfulness and accuracy of certain statements."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 28}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 72}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Restructuring Term Sheet is a document outlining the terms of the restructuring plan, which the Company must adhere to unless modified with consent."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring Term Sheet is a document that contains the terms and conditions related to the restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring Term Sheet is a document that outlines the terms and conditions of the restructuring agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring Term Sheet is a document that outlines the terms of the proposed restructuring plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring Term Sheet is a document that sets forth certain terms and conditions, including the Company’s rights regarding Alternative Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring Term Sheet outlines the key terms and conditions of the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09b10f93e9533caaeadef2357fac4779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EFFECTIVE PERIOD&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Effective Period is a defined period during which the Company agrees to certain commitments, including seeking approval of the Plan and completing the Restructuring."&lt;SEP&gt;"Effective Period is the duration during which the Supporting Lenders agree to support restructuring efforts under the terms of the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 5}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 31}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Plan is a detailed proposal for restructuring, which the Company agrees to seek approval for during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"Plan is a proposed course of action that requires acceptance by Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Plan is a restructuring plan proposed by the Company, which may be withdrawn or revoked."&lt;SEP&gt;"Plan is a set of actions or procedures, likely related to a bankruptcy or restructuring process, with specific releases and exculpations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Plan is a specific agreement or proposal that the organizations are supporting or modifying as per the agreement terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Plan is a specific proposal or strategy that needs approval, possibly related to restructuring or other significant changes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-07a778754579048a8dc70de19952fd25&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c7e4c4e232c720e82d3c8e3199df150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 24}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CONFIRMATION ORDER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Confirmation Order is a legal document confirming the terms of the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Confirmation Order is an order confirming the Plan, which the Company agrees to support and defend in appeals."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 25}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 66}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;DEFINITIVE DOCUMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"DOCUMENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Definitive Documents are documents that need to be negotiated in good faith by the Company during the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are legal documents that formalize the terms of the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are the agreements and documents that need to be negotiated in good faith by the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are the final agreements and documents that need to be negotiated in good faith by the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Definitive Documents are the final agreements or documents that must be consistent with the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 63}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUBSIDIARIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Subsidiaries are affiliated organizations under the Company, also subject to the same conditions and compliance requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are organizations that are controlled by the Company and are part of the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the main Company mentioned in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Subsidiaries are subsidiary organizations under the main Company, which also need to comply with the same conditions and possess necessary permits."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a3118a5b7ebfcd2e890ae61fb2869a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecc6c7a82dfa782ad734c65afdc66563&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c27bf2a240355db951cca111fcbf0b4</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 20}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Affiliates are organizations that are related to the Company and its Subsidiaries and are also part of the Restructuring process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations that are associated with the Company, and their compliance is also important."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations that are not subsidiaries but still have some form of association with the main Company mentioned in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations to the Company and its Subsidiaries, also subject to the same conditions and compliance requirements."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations to the Company and its Subsidiaries, also subject to the same conditions and regulations as the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related organizations under the same corporate umbrella as the Company."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9c27bf2a240355db951cca111fcbf0b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3118a5b7ebfcd2e890ae61fb2869a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b75be069c2e11b99b8211d14f57d5a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecc6c7a82dfa782ad734c65afdc66563</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 20}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;OTHER PARTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Other Parties include all parties involved in the Restructuring process except the Company and its Subsidiaries and Affiliates."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;ALTERNATIVE TRANSACTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Alternative Transactions are other possible transactions that the Company has the right to pursue, as specified in the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 3}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 18}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 62}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RESTRUCTURING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Restructuring is a process involving the reorganization of a company's financial affairs, including the filing of certain documents with the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is a process mentioned in the context of the agreement, implying significant changes or adjustments."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is the process of reorganizing the Company's financial structure, including the Plan and the Restructuring Term Sheet."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is the process of reorganizing the financial affairs of the Debtors to avoid liquidation or bankruptcy."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring is the process of reorganizing the financial and operational structure of a company to improve its financial health."&lt;SEP&gt;"Restructuring refers to a significant business process involving negotiations, coordination, and compliance with various milestones and agreements."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b2a5cf3b4f7ee70356b1bcc75677b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01a7b92c0bded7877f99a6813c111de0</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 4}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 25}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 66}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Supporting Lenders are financial institutions or lenders who are parties to an agreement and have certain rights and remedies as outlined in the text."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are involved in the consultation process regarding the assumption or rejection of executory contracts and unexpired leases of non-residential real property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties involved in a restructuring plan and need to be informed about certain filings."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties involved in the restructuring process, providing support and negotiation for Definitive Documents."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are parties to an agreement with specific obligations and rights related to the timely satisfaction of conditions and voting on a plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the financial institutions providing support to the Debtors during restructuring."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the lenders that need to be consulted regarding the assumption or rejection of executory contracts and unexpired leases of non-residential real property."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the lenders that provide notice of inconsistencies in the Definitive Documents and require corrections within three Business Days."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties agreeing to support restructuring efforts under the terms of the Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties that provide financial support to the Company and have certain rights and obligations under the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties to whom the Company must provide certain documents before filing with the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders are the parties who have entered into the Agreement and whose costs and efforts are related to the Expense Reimbursement Amount."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders refer to a group of lenders who deliver a notice leading to the automatic termination of an agreement."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-52108fe481d472cc1ff728e87732c8fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a084f2e9cb7d42ed40a5f082d5224a62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-32b2a5cf3b4f7ee70356b1bcc75677b8&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09b10f93e9533caaeadef2357fac4779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01a7b92c0bded7877f99a6813c111de0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f645c16a1cbf2169e4377767b2bca09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-752a4bcfd49e3f7ebeb351081eb4553f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7c7e4c4e232c720e82d3c8e3199df150&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-78ab64a815cd3d2a836336392f2eca48</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 5}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 31}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;BEES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Bees are a group of insects that are part of the installation process for a beehive, potentially causing disturbance during the setup."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are insects that form a colony and produce honey, managed in hives."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are part of a busy colony that rely on an adequate food supply from the feeder to perform various activities such as wax secretion, comb drawing, and brood raising."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are social insects that form colonies and are managed within hives, responsible for pollination and brood rearing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the individual members of the colony, working together to maintain and grow the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the insects that make up the hive, including the queen, workers, and drones.""&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the members of the hive colony responsible for various tasks such as feeding, drawing out frames, and occupying hive bodies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the workers in the hive, responsible for various tasks such as gathering nectar and caring for the queen and larvae."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the workers of the colony, responsible for various tasks such as foraging, caring for the brood, and maintaining the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees are the workers of the hive and are responsible for defending their space from potential robbers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees refer to the worker bees that accompany the queen in the queen cage and serve as her attendants."&lt;SEP&gt;"Worker bees that accompany the queen in the queen cage."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bf1cda15c3e18b5b766dda26758bb950&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-409158f771708f639ac427a52dff0ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c6642003e1962771aafdc3360a347d3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9adb318b0497cb51bfeea12fbe24d4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4807ea62df150b7fa65c431a05d04369&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fc143771bbf22129f9c2b7602fb6cc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58e222836a11d1f2b7225f57ea3fe864&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a10e4014c4f193eee14a336747f04aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01a7b92c0bded7877f99a6813c111de0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-815f215becbebf90c088cce626290fc0</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 52}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 78}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUEEN EXCLUDER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Queen Excluder is a device used in beekeeping to prevent the queen bee from laying eggs in certain parts of the hive."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 54}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HONEY EXTRACTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Honey Extractors are tools or methods used to extract honey from beehives, facilitating the process of honey collection."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey Extractors are tools used in beekeeping to remove honey from the combs without damaging the hive structure."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 54}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"LOCATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A hive is a structure where bees live and maintain their colony, typically managed by beekeepers."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is a structure where bees live and store honey, and its presence can trigger defensive reactions from bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the dwelling place of a bee colony, where they store honey and raise their young."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the final destination where the bees will settle after installation."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the home of the bee colony, where the queen and worker bees live and produce honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the living space and social structure of the colony where bees live and perform various tasks."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the living space of the beehive colony, containing the queen, workers, and brood.""&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the structure where bees live and perform their dances."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the structure where bees live and produce honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the structure where the bees live and work, organized efficiently by the bees themselves."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive is the structure where the colony lives and produces brood and honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Hive refers to a bee colony organized into a structure with multiple bodies for housing and storing resources."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Hive is the physical structure where the bees live and work, including the queen, drones, and workers."&lt;SEP&gt;"The hive is the main structure where bees live and store their food, and it needs protection from potential robbers."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-409158f771708f639ac427a52dff0ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bf1cda15c3e18b5b766dda26758bb950&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-35887a077ff8cc664c022e0850b536e3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c6642003e1962771aafdc3360a347d3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e9adb318b0497cb51bfeea12fbe24d4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fc143771bbf22129f9c2b7602fb6cc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58e222836a11d1f2b7225f57ea3fe864&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-796f45a52ffa07aa91bbe739a0f9329d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c25c7431109863bb945279517ed9aab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-01a7b92c0bded7877f99a6813c111de0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-752a4bcfd49e3f7ebeb351081eb4553f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-815f215becbebf90c088cce626290fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1073b6d62431432ec578fe2bf1d1f663</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 13}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 57}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 87}]</data>
</node>
