  <data key="d2">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;QUEEN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Queen is a crucial figure in the bee colony, responsible for laying eggs and ensuring the growth of the colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the female bee responsible for laying eggs and maintaining the colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the female bee that lays eggs and is kept from laying eggs in honey supers by a Queen Excluder."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the female reproductive member of the bee colony, recognized by her larger size and longer abdomen compared to worker bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the reproductive female bee that lays eggs and is cared for by the worker bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"Queen is the reproductive female of the beehive, responsible for laying eggs.""&lt;SEP&gt;"The Queen is the mother of the colony, laying eggs and ensuring the survival and growth of the colony."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bf1cda15c3e18b5b766dda26758bb950&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8fc143771bbf22129f9c2b7602fb6cc5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4807ea62df150b7fa65c431a05d04369&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c25c7431109863bb945279517ed9aab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-815f215becbebf90c088cce626290fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1073b6d62431432ec578fe2bf1d1f663</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 56}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 83}]</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;HONEY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PRODUCT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Honey is a sweet substance produced by bees from nectar and stored in the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is a sweet, viscous substance produced by bees from nectar, used for consumption and commercial purposes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is stored within the comb by the bees.""&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is the sweet substance produced by bees and stored in the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Honey is the sweet substance produced by bees from nectar, used for food and medicinal purposes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-bf1cda15c3e18b5b766dda26758bb950&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-409158f771708f639ac427a52dff0ac0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1073b6d62431432ec578fe2bf1d1f663</data>
  <data key="d3">[{"level": 0, "cluster": 12}, {"level": 1, "cluster": 55}, {"level": 2, "cluster": 81}]</data>
</node>
