<node id="&quot;WAX&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"MATERIAL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Wax is a natural material produced by bees to construct the comb structure of the hive."&lt;SEP&gt;"Wax is the material used by bees to construct the comb."</data>
