</node>
<node id="&quot;LANGSTROTH'S DISCOVERY&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Langstroth's Discovery refers to the invention of the movable frame beehive, which revolutionized beekeeping by allowing for easier hive manipulation and larger honey crops."&lt;SEP&gt;"Langstroth's discovery refers to the invention of the movable frame beehive, which revolutionized beekeeping practices."</data>
