  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Federal Research Facilities are institutions funded by the government to conduct research on various topics, including beekeeping and apiculture."&lt;SEP&gt;"Federal research facilities are institutions that developed agricultural components and contributed to the advancement of apiculture through research and education."</data>
