</node>
<node id="&quot;COLLEGES AND UNIVERSITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Colleges and universities offer coursework and degrees related to apiculture, contributing to the education and training of beekeepers."</data>
