</node>
<node id="&quot;ISOLEUCINE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"TECHNOLOGY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Isoleucine is a specific substrate that inhibits the enzyme Monod was studying."&lt;SEP&gt;"Isoleucine is an amino acid that does not fit into the active pocket of the enzyme, unlike threonine."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-95d378a4a5d837b5df62cf1349844f34&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a1fe5c5c561e507d8c235678840d518</data>
