<node id="&quot;ALLOSTERIC REGULATION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Allosteric Regulation is the phenomenon where the binding of a molecule at a site other than the active site alters the shape of the enzyme, affecting its function."</data>
