</node>
<node id="&quot;FEEDER CAN&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Feeder can is a container used to provide food to the queen and worker bees within the queen cage."&lt;SEP&gt;"Feeder can is a container within the package that provides food for the bees during the initial stages of installation."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-e9adb318b0497cb51bfeea12fbe24d4a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4807ea62df150b7fa65c431a05d04369</data>
