  <data key="d0">"CHEMICAL"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Inducer is a substance that triggers the production of enzymes in bacteria, specifically mentioned as sugar in the context of the feeding of bees."&lt;SEP&gt;"The inducer is a substance that positively controls enzyme synthesis, initially thought to be related to the mechanism."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-1a10e4014c4f193eee14a336747f04aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-babaf934dcb765f08d028d1b33488eef</data>
