</node>
<node id="&quot;ENZYME GENE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The enzyme gene is a segment of DNA responsible for encoding the instructions to produce the enzyme needed to break down lactose."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-22254c52213838b97f2638a84916771e</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;CAR MOVING DOWN THE STREET&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"CONCEPT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The car moving down the street is used as an analogy to explain the direct causality people tend to assume in everyday observations."</data>
