  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VISUALIZATION TECHNIQUES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Visualization Techniques are a treatment modality used to address MPA, benefiting elite physical performance athletes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Visualization Techniques benefit Elite Physical Performance Athletes in addressing MPA."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PSYCHOLOGICAL READINESS TRAINING&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Psychological Readiness Training benefits Elite Physical Performance Athletes in addressing MPA."&lt;SEP&gt;"Psychological Readiness Training is a treatment modality used to address MPA, benefiting elite physical performance athletes."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;STAGE FRIGHT&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Stage Fright is a condition within the performing arts community that may be considered a weakness or character flaw, affecting vocal performance."&lt;SEP&gt;"Stage Fright is considered a weakness or character flaw within the Performing Arts Community."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOCAL ATHLETES&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vocal Athletes are performers who require mental preparation for optimal competition and performance, similar to physical athletes."&lt;SEP&gt;"Vocal Athletes require Mental Preparation for optimal competition and performance."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EMOTIONAL RESPONSE CONTROL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Emotional Response Control is a skill that vocal athletes may need to learn to convey emotion without eliciting an internal emotional response."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;EXPERIENCED PSYCHOLOGIST&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Experienced Psychologists can help Vocal Athletes control and understand MPA."&lt;SEP&gt;"Experienced Psychologists may help change ingrained neural pathways for vocal athletes to control and understand MPA."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOCAL INJURY PREVENTION&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Vocal Injury Prevention involves understanding Common Causes of Voice Disorders and taking preventive measures."&lt;SEP&gt;"Vocal Injury Prevention involves understanding common causes of voice disorders and taking preventive measures."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;VOICE DISORDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"EVENT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Voice Disorders are caused by vocally abusive behaviors or misuse of the voice, including phonot"&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice Disorders are conditions that can affect vocal performance, often due to misuse or abuse."&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice Disorders can result from Vocal Abuse."&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice Disorders can result from Vocally Abusive Behaviors or misuse of the voice."&lt;SEP&gt;"Voice Disorders encompass a range of conditions affecting the voice, including those caused by vocally abusive behaviors and chronic or suboptimal vocal properties."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-7f6dfd6cf19346b800ac411171835010&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-98146bc44ee4d6b982895f8ab196757a</data>
</node>
