  <data key="d5">"Events are important for beekeepers to participate in."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;COMMUNITY SUPPORT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Community support is important for beekeepers to have."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;REGULAR READING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Regular reading is important for beekeepers to stay informed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;POLLINATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers rely on pollination to ensure the success of their crops, which is essential for their livelihood."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;CROP&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers manage honey bee colonies to protect and enhance crop yields through pollination."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;DISEASE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers must monitor and address diseases in their colonies to maintain their health and prevent colony collapse."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;DROUGHT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers need to manage their colonies during drought periods to ensure they have sufficient water and resources."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;HARSH WINTER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers take precautions during harsh winters to protect their colonies from extreme cold and potential loss."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;PREDATORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers must protect their colonies from predators to ensure the survival of their honey bee populations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;NORTH AMERICA&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers in North America face unique challenges due to the region's climate and geography, including disease, drought, and harsh winters."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;COLONY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers manage and care for honey bee colonies to ensure their health and productivity."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;FERAL COLONIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers may encounter feral colonies and sometimes attempt to manage them or integrate them into their operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;HONEY BEE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers work with honey bees to manage and protect their colonies."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;QUEEN BEE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers focus on maintaining the health and productivity of queen bees to ensure strong colonies."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;WORKER BEE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers manage the activities of worker bees to ensure efficient hive operations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;BEARS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers must protect their colonies from bear attacks, which can be a significant threat."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;BIRDS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers must protect their colonies from bird attacks, which can also be a significant threat."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;RESEARCH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers rely on research to understand and address the challenges faced by their colonies."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;MANAGEMENT PRACTICES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers apply management practices to ensure the health and productivity of their colonies."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;DYNAMIC ENDEAVOR&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping is a dynamic endeavor that requires continuous adaptation and learning to address new challenges."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;PROBLEMS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers face various problems, such as disease, drought, and harsh winters, which require solutions and management."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;SOLUTIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers develop and implement solutions to address the challenges they face in beekeeping."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;RECENT YEARS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers have seen significant increases in knowledge and problem-solving capabilities in recent years."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;OUT OF TOUCH&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers who are out of touch with the latest developments in beekeeping may struggle to manage their colonies effectively."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;COLLECTIVE INTROSPECTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers engage in collective introspection to reflect on their roles and responsibilities in the broader context of beekeeping."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;COSMIC PLAY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers operate within a larger context, or 'cosmic play,' that includes the broader universe of beekeeping and its impact on human history."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;HUMAN HISTORY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping has a significant impact on human history, shaping the development of human civilization."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;ENCRYPTED DIALOGUE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers may engage in secure and complex communication, or 'encrypted dialogue,' to share information and coordinate efforts."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;INTRICATE PATTERNS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers study the intricate patterns of behavior and interaction within honey bee colonies to better understand and manage them."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;UNCANNY ANTICIPATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers may anticipate and prepare for future events or behaviors based on their understanding of honey bee colonies."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-4957ec7ee118ac56c14f04d82744a8e6</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPER&quot;" target="&quot;DANCE LANGUAGE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeepers rely on the dance language to understand the needs and actions of the bee colony."|</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-796f45a52ffa07aa91bbe739a0f9329d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEHAVER&quot;" target="&quot;GOVERNMENT AGENCY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beehavers may also rely on government agencies for resources and support, though they may not fully utilize them."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEHAVER&quot;" target="&quot;UNIVERSITY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beehavers may not fully engage with the research and expertise provided by universities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEHAVER&quot;" target="&quot;LOCAL BEEKEEPER ORGANIZATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beehavers may not fully engage with local beekeeper organizations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-2bd4cd24e118c8cfdf44ccab7c205d81</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
