  <data key="d4">20.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"A bee acts as a dancer in the hive, performing a dance to communicate the location of food sources to other bees."&lt;&lt;SEP&gt;"A dancer is a type of bee that performs the dance to communicate information."&lt;</data>
