<edge source="&quot;BANKRUPTCY COURT&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDER&quot;">
  <data key="d4">53.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bankruptcy Court oversees the actions of Supporting Lenders, including their ability to transfer claims."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bankruptcy Court requires permission for Supporting Lenders to change or withdraw their votes in favor of the Plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lender must negotiate in good faith with the Bankruptcy Court to address legal or structural impediments."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court may limit transfers of Prepetition Agreement Claims by Supporting Lenders."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-07a778754579048a8dc70de19952fd25&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2e4d27c8d8b004a26dce6446ca790153&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
