  <data key="d4">32.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders need to be informed about certain filings to the Bankruptcy Court at least two Business Days prior to filing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders provide input on certain filings to the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court's calendar affects the negotiations and extensions of milestones by the Supporting Lenders."</data>
