</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BANKRUPTCY COURT&quot;" target="&quot;COMPANY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">58.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company intends to file various motions and pleadings with the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court can appoint trustees, receivers, or examiners to operate and manage the Company’s businesses if it enters an unstayed Order."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court has jurisdiction over the Company and can appoint trustees, receivers, or examiners."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company must ensure that the Expense Reimbursement Amount is treated as an administrative expense by the Bankruptcy Court."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-8f645c16a1cbf2169e4377767b2bca09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BANKRUPTCY COURT&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">75.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors are subject to the jurisdiction of the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors must file documents and objections with the Bankruptcy Court as per the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court has jurisdiction over the Debtors and can appoint trustees, receivers, or examiners."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Bankruptcy Court has the authority to appoint trustees, receivers, or examiners to operate and manage the Debtors’ businesses."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Debtors must ensure that the Bankruptcy Court approves the treatment of the Expense Reimbursement Amount as an administrative expense."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f645c16a1cbf2169e4377767b2bca09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
