  <data key="d4">52.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lender can transfer Prepetition Agreement Claims to Transferees, who agree to be bound by the terms of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lender can transfer claims to Transferees, who agree to be bound by the terms of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting Lenders may transfer their Prepetition Agreement Claims to Transferees, who then become Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"Supporting lender can transfer claims to transferees, who agree to be bound by the terms of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Transferee is deemed to make representations and warranties of a Supporting Lender upon consummation of a Transfer."</data>
