  <data key="d4">21.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company supports and does not object to changes or withdrawals of votes by Supporting Lenders, as required by the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company agrees to support and not object to changes or withdrawals of votes or releases by the Supporting Lender as per the agreement terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is involved in receiving and managing Transferee Joinders from Supporting Lenders."</data>
