<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;">
  <data key="d4">63.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company agrees to the terms and conditions set forth in the Restructuring Term Sheet, including its rights regarding Alternative Transactions."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is subject to the terms outlined in the Restructuring Term Sheet, which are referenced in the agreement and include fee and expense terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company must adhere to the terms and conditions outlined in the Restructuring Term Sheet, which must be consistent with the Definitive Documents."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company must adhere to the terms set forth in the Restructuring Term Sheet unless modified with consent."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-09b10f93e9533caaeadef2357fac4779&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;PLAN&quot;">
  <data key="d4">29.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company agrees to use commercially reasonable efforts to seek approval of the Plan during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company may withdraw or revoke the Plan, or file alternative transactions that are inconsistent with the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b027a389b731df576108e8ab044165a</data>
