</edge>
<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;AFFILIATES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">71.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Affiliates are related organizations that are associated with the Company, and their compliance is also important."&lt;SEP&gt;"Affiliates are related to the Company and must comply with the same conditions and regulations as the Company."&lt;SEP&gt;"Company directs its Affiliates to participate in the Restructuring process during the Effective Period."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company mentioned in the text has Affiliates that are related organizations with some form of association."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a3118a5b7ebfcd2e890ae61fb2869a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d5417895366679d5abd3d326e6c67df2&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecc6c7a82dfa782ad734c65afdc66563&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c27bf2a240355db951cca111fcbf0b4</data>
