  <data key="d4">72.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company must provide certain documents to Supporting Lenders before filing with the Bankruptcy Court."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company is obligated to pay the fees and expenses of the Supporting Lenders, and failure to do so within three Business Days results in automatic termination of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company must correct inconsistencies in the Definitive Documents within three Business Days after notice from the Supporting Lenders."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company receives notifications from the Supporting Lenders regarding events that may affect the agreement."</data>
