<edge source="&quot;COMPANY&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">99.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Company and Debtors are involved in the same bankruptcy proceedings and must adhere to the agreement terms."&lt;SEP&gt;"Debtors and Company are part of the same agreement, with Debtors paying the Expense Reimbursement Amount and Company supporting the plan."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and Debtors are involved in bankruptcy proceedings, with the Bankruptcy Court having the authority to grant relief terminating, annulling, or modifying the automatic stay."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and Debtors are part of the same agreement, with the Company supporting the plan and the Debtors paying the Expense Reimbursement Amount upon termination."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company and its Subsidiaries are subject to conditions and notices from Debtors, but no specific relationship is detailed."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Company mentioned in the text has Debtors who owe money or have obligations to the company."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Knowledge of the Debtors is considered in assessing compliance with conditions and permits."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-9c27bf2a240355db951cca111fcbf0b4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a3118a5b7ebfcd2e890ae61fb2869a29&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecc6c7a82dfa782ad734c65afdc66563&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f645c16a1cbf2169e4377767b2bca09&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5</data>
