  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Claims are held by Parties in the agreement, such as Supporting Lenders or Transferees."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Parties in the agreement make Representations and Warranties regarding their claims and obligations."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-e243a6e605d9bda590d41e79f0bdcf6a</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders must ensure that their representations and warranties remain true and accurate."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;" target="&quot;RESTRUCTURING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Restructuring Term Sheet outlines the key terms and conditions of the Restructuring process."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders must comply with the terms and conditions specified in the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;RESTRUCTURING TERM SHEET&quot;" target="&quot;DEFINITIVE DOCUMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Definitive Documents must be consistent with the Restructuring Term Sheet."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-497066cb85846685befbf13ad5fbcafa</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EFFECTIVE PERIOD&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders agree to support restructuring efforts during the Effective Period."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PLAN&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Supporting Lenders must vote to accept the Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-7c7e4c4e232c720e82d3c8e3199df150</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PLAN&quot;" target="&quot;AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Agreement and Plan are interconnected, with the Agreement containing terms that affect the Plan."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-07a778754579048a8dc70de19952fd25</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PLAN&quot;" target="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;">
  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party has the right to take actions related to the Plan, as outlined in the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;PLAN&quot;" target="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors are involved in the Plan and are required to pay the Expense Reimbursement Amount upon termination of the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-601adfca36708dd405154d57329e95d5</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
