  <data key="d4">27.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Supporting Lenders are bound by the terms and conditions outlined in the Agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Supporting Lenders have entered into the Agreement based on their obligation to pay the Expense Reimbursement Amount."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a084f2e9cb7d42ed40a5f082d5224a62&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a98abc7661191612db1330d484a309bd</data>
