  <data key="d4">69.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Bees are the members of the Hive colony, performing various tasks to maintain and expand the hive structure."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and maintain their colony within a hive, performing tasks such as pollination and brood rearing."|&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within the Hive to produce honey."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within the hive, maintaining its organization and efficiency."&lt;SEP&gt;"Bees live and work within the hive."|</data>
