  <data key="d5">"Queen is the female bee that leads the colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"The queen guides the bees in maintaining and growing the colony."&lt;SEP&gt;"The queen is surrounded by worker bees in the queen cage, who keep her groomed and fed."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a6fe41559fa35bb0034a3d53d2587c5f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-815f215becbebf90c088cce626290fc0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4807ea62df150b7fa65c431a05d04369</data>
