  <data key="d5">"Brood nests are located within frames where the queen lays eggs and young bees develop."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-1c25c7431109863bb945279517ed9aab</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LANGSTROTH'S DISCOVERY&quot;" target="&quot;MOVABLE FRAME BEEHIVE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Langstroth's Discovery led to the invention of the Movable Frame Beehive, which transformed traditional beekeeping practices."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LANGSTROTH'S DISCOVERY&quot;" target="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;">
  <data key="d4">10.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Langstroth's Discovery revolutionized Beekeeping by introducing the Movable Frame Beehive, enabling easier hive management and larger honey yields."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;LANGSTROTH'S DISCOVERY&quot;" target="&quot;INDUSTRIAL REVOLUTION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Langstroth's discovery of the movable frame beehive played a crucial role in the Industrial Revolution by improving beekeeping efficiency and practices."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-90bb6316aa4aebbba7c436b6735776e9</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;" target="&quot;ACADEMIC INTEREST&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Beekeeping gained academic interest as more institutions began offering courses and degrees in apiculture."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;" target="&quot;GOVERNMENT INTEREST&quot;">
  <data key="d4">6.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Government Interest in beekeeping increased as larger honey crops became common and bees were used more for commercial crop pollination."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;" target="&quot;FEDERAL RESEARCH FACILITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Federal Research Facilities developed in response to growing interest in beekeeping, focusing on scientific research in apiculture."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;BEEKEEPING&quot;" target="&quot;COMMERCIAL OPERATIONS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">9.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Commercial Operations emerged as a result of advancements in beekeeping, leading to large-scale honey production and sales."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;ACADEMIC INTEREST&quot;" target="&quot;GOVERNMENT INTEREST&quot;">
  <data key="d4">7.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Academic and Government Interest in beekeeping grew concurrently, with both sectors investing in research and development."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;GOVERNMENT INTEREST&quot;" target="&quot;FEDERAL RESEARCH FACILITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Government Interest supported the development of Federal Research Facilities dedicated to studying beekeeping and apiculture."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-cea2d10b8f63096775e979aa558ddd87</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
