  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors' material assets can only be accessed or used with the consent of the DIP Agent."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-09b10f93e9533caaeadef2357fac4779</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;" target="&quot;PERSON&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors may face objections from Persons in the Bankruptcy Court regarding the use of cash collateral, proceeds, or adequate protection."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;" target="&quot;DIP ORDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors must comply with the DIP Orders, which grant the use of cash collateral or adequate protection to the Prepetition Lenders."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;DEBTORS&quot;" target="&quot;PREPETITION LENDERS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Debtors must respond to objections filed by Prepetition Lenders regarding the use of cash collateral, proceeds, or adequate protection."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-19f1f2ac97e350d7978ba6d7f910d3d7</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EFFECTIVE DATE&quot;" target="&quot;CONDITIONS SET FORTH IN ARTICLE VIII&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Effective Date is the date by which the conditions set forth in Article VIII must be satisfied."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-52108fe481d472cc1ff728e87732c8fb</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 9.1&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Transactions are the subject of the conditions outlined in Section 9.1."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-78ab64a815cd3d2a836336392f2eca48</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;TRANSACTIONS&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 9.3&quot;">
  <data key="d4">8.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Transactions are the subject of the clauses outlined in Section 9.3."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-78ab64a815cd3d2a836336392f2eca48</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;FEES AND EXPENSES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party is responsible for paying fees and expenses up to the date of termination."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 10.13&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party must adhere to the terms of Section 10.13 regarding the payment of fees and expenses."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;TERMINATION&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party is released from its commitments upon termination of the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;RELEASE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party is released from its commitments and can take actions related to the release, as outlined in the agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EACH PARTY&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDER'S VOTE&quot;">
  <data key="d4">14.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Each Party must support and not object to changes or withdrawals of Supporting Lender's votes, as required by the Bankruptcy Court."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-f1048bb352f0f09318b7c1004aeb9e1d</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPENSE REIMBURSEMENT AMOUNT&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS' COSTS AND EFFORTS&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Expense Reimbursement Amount is reasonable in relation to the Supporting Lenders' costs and efforts."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a084f2e9cb7d42ed40a5f082d5224a62</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPENSE REIMBURSEMENT AMOUNT&quot;" target="&quot;SUPPORTING LENDERS' LOST OPPORTUNITIES&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Expense Reimbursement Amount compensates for the Supporting Lenders' lost opportunities."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a084f2e9cb7d42ed40a5f082d5224a62</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPENSE REIMBURSEMENT AMOUNT&quot;" target="&quot;TRANSACTIONS CONTEMPLATED BY THIS AGREEMENT&quot;">
  <data key="d4">18.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"The Expense Reimbursement Amount is an integral part of the transactions contemplated by the Agreement."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-a084f2e9cb7d42ed40a5f082d5224a62</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;EXPENSE REIMBURSEMENT AMOUNT&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 9.3&quot;">
  <data key="d4">26.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Section 9.3 outlines the specific amount and conditions for the Expense Reimbursement Amount."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Expense Reimbursement Amount is a specific monetary amount as outlined in Section 9.3."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-78ab64a815cd3d2a836336392f2eca48</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
<edge source="&quot;SECTION 9.1&quot;" target="&quot;SECTION 9.3&quot;">
  <data key="d4">16.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Section 9.1 and Section 9.3 work together to outline the terms and conditions of the agreement."&lt;SEP&gt;"Section 9.3 provides further details on the conditions outlined in Section 9.1."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-78ab64a815cd3d2a836336392f2eca48</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
