  <data key="d4">12.0</data>
  <data key="d5">"Monod and his collaborators initially thought the inducer positively controlled enzyme synthesis, which led to their initial logic."</data>
  <data key="d6">chunk-babaf934dcb765f08d028d1b33488eef</data>
  <data key="d7">1</data>
</edge>
